         <abstract>
            <p>We show how to obtain continuity in the &lt;tex-math&gt;$\operatorname{BV}(\Omega)$&lt;/tex-math&gt;-seminorm of the L&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;-projection of &lt;tex-math&gt;$u \in \operatorname{BV}(\Omega)$&lt;/tex-math&gt; into a large class of finite element spaces.</p>
          </abstract>
